title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland-Alameda County Coliseum on 1994-12-09
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger, Stagger Lee, The Same Thing, Loose Lucy, El Paso*, Broken Arrow, Ramble On Rose, The Music Never Stopped

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain, Way to Go Home, Truckin'-> That Would Be Something-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Space-> Box Of Rain, E: Johnny B. Goode

* Weir on acoustic guitar
